@sov_struggle

The ascension of Joseph Stalin to *General-Secretary* of the <span style="color: #bf0000">**Union**</span> has vastly complicated our ties to the span style="color: #800000">**International**</span>. Though seemingly still on the surface, murmurs of Stalin's movements and actions have not gone unnoticed by us, nor have their intentions. 

We cannot let the <span style="color: #800000">**Communist International**</span> become a playground for the <span style="color: #bf0000">**Soviet Union**</span>.

